data.description: OPEN FLOOR PLAN & HIGH CEILINGS THROUGHOUT THIS 4 BED, 2 BATH, 1,982 SQFT. HOUSE ON .517 OF AN ACRE. FULLY FENCED YARD WITH DOUBLE DOOR GATE TO BACKYARD & GORGEOUS LARGE TREES. STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCE PACKAGE AT KITCHEN, INCLUDING REFRIDGERATOR. 42" UPPER CABINETS AT KITCHEN. WHITE QUARTZ COUNTERTOP IN KITCHEN AND BATH. SEPERATE TUB & SHOWER IN MASTER BATH. DOUBLE WALK IN CLOSET IN MASTER. DOUBLE UNDERMOUNT SINKS, 36" COUNTER HEIGHT AND BANK OF DRAWERS IN BOTH BATHS. DOUBLE PANE LOW-E WINDOWS. SPRAY FOAM INSULATION THROUGHOUT THE HOME. CARPET IN BEDROOMS & CERAMIC TILE THROUGHOUT. CEILING FANS IN ALL BEDROOMS. FINISHED GARAGE & GARAGE DOOR OPENER. 20FT WIDE DRIVEWAY. COVERED FRONT AND BACK PORCH WITH CUSTOM RAILING & CEDAR PLANK CEILING. LOW TAX RATE, LOCATED JUST EAST OF AUSTIN BEHIND CIRCUIT OF THE AMERICAS. VA ASSUMPTION OPTION.
